{"tid":2414833,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國毅力號火星探測器成功著陸火星","createTime":"2021-02-19T17:05:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-23T02:43:34.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8ce132dec778b36dadd285719d585fa2fddd9531","tid":2414833,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T17:05:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1576326-20210219.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1576326-20210219.htm&d=VW1JDW%2BJF%2FyRlCRofLrhGllsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=c4b21154\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1576326-20210219.htm&h=67db7424\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1576326-20210219.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n美國太空總署的火星探測器毅力號，成功在火星赤道以北的耶澤羅隕石坑著陸，並向地面傳回照片。<br />\n<br />\n毅力號配備特殊設計的傳感器，以及自主飛行的小型無人機，主要任務是分析火星的地理與環境特徵，以及採集岩石與沉積物樣本，期望在火星表面，找到古老微生物的證據。<br />\n<br />\n毅力號去年7月從佛羅里達州卡納維拉爾角基地，由擎天神5號火箭搭載升空，毅力號降落到火星時，需要急劇減速，這段時間被科學家稱為恐怖7分鐘。"},{"pid":"ae8bb964fb5d6653582aa146931d83086b4ee6ab","tid":2414833,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T17:08:35.000Z","msg":"好事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可惜依家係戀童政府"},{"pid":"56c0b5dc796219df25d52ef95c5186f6a6de05d1","tid":2414833,"uid":9594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T17:10:42.000Z","msg":"此時一隻躲在探測器上的蟑螂爬了出來"},{"pid":"bff2e0c79ee6653fe819a548853008304d5d18fb","tid":2414833,"uid":3358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"56c0b5dc796219df25d52ef95c5186f6a6de05d1","tid":2414833,"uid":9594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T17:10:42.000Z","msg":"此時一隻躲在探測器上的蟑螂爬了出來"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T17:13:35.000Z",